<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Cloudpods – 操作指南</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/</link><description>Recent content in 操作指南 on Cloudpods</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs: 创建</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/create/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/create/</guid><description>
&lt;h2 id="前提条件">前提条件&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>录入云账号&lt;/li>
&lt;li>当前用户为系统管理员或域管理员&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="操作步骤">操作步骤&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">&lt;a data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link active" href="#tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-0" role="tab" aria-controls="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-0" aria-selected="true">控制台新建&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li class="nav-item">&lt;a data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link" href="#tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-1" role="tab" aria-controls="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-1">命令行新建&lt;/a>&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1">&lt;div id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-0" class="tab-pane show active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-0">
&lt;p>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>登录控制台, 选择 [多云管理] -&amp;gt; [云用户组], 进入云用户组列表页面&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>点击左上角 [新建] 按钮&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>根据页面提示信息, 配置以下信息&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th>类别&lt;/th>
&lt;th>必选/可选&lt;/th>
&lt;th>说明&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>域&lt;/td>
&lt;td>必选&lt;/td>
&lt;td>仅管理后台可见, 域管理后台默认使用当前用户所在域&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>名称&lt;/td>
&lt;td>必选&lt;/td>
&lt;td>用户组名称标识&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>平台&lt;/td>
&lt;td>必选&lt;/td>
&lt;td>控制台根据云账号录入账号自动选择支持的平台，若第一次录入云账号，需要刷新整个页面，清除缓存后，可以看到云账号所在的平台&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>权限&lt;/td>
&lt;td>可选&lt;/td>
&lt;td>可以根据平台选择相应的权限, 若不指定, 则用户组无任何权限&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>点击确定即可创建云用户组&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-1" class="tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialcreate-1-1">
&lt;p>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">
climc cloud-group-create &amp;lt;Name&amp;gt; &amp;lt;Provider&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
&lt;h4 class="alert-heading">注意&lt;/h4>
新创建的云用户组并不会立即到公有云上创建相应的资源
只有当用户组被公有云子账号使用时, 才会到公有云创建相应的资源
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Docs: 删除</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/delete/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/delete/</guid><description>
&lt;h2 id="操作步骤">操作步骤&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">&lt;a data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link active" href="#tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-0" role="tab" aria-controls="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-0" aria-selected="true">控制台删除&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li class="nav-item">&lt;a data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link" href="#tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-1" role="tab" aria-controls="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-1">命令行删除&lt;/a>&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1">&lt;div id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-0" class="tab-pane show active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-0">
&lt;p>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">
1. 登录控制台, 选择 &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>多云管理&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> -&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>云用户组&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span>, 进入云用户组列表页面
2. 找到待删除的云用户组，点击右侧 &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>更多&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> -&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>删除&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> 按钮
3. 点击 &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>确定&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> 按钮删除
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;div id="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-1" class="tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabset-zhdocshowtomulticloudcloudgrouptutorialdelete-1-1">
&lt;p>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">
climc cloud-group-delete &amp;lt;云用户组名称或id&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
&lt;h4 class="alert-heading">注意&lt;/h4>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>删除云用户组会真实删除云上相应的资源&lt;/li>
&lt;li>可查看云用户组权限组缓存列表查看当前云用户组和各个云账号上面的资源映射&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Docs: 关联云用户</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/clouduser/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/clouduser/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Docs: 关联权限</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/cloudpolicy/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/cloudpolicy/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Docs: 同步状态</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/sync/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jun 2021 08:22:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/howto/multicloud/cloudgroup/tutorial/sync/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>